sprang out of that decade

00:04:19.579 --> 00:04:21.410
and ran into the '70s.

00:04:21.410 --> 00:04:26.510
And it became one of the clarion
calls to our personal lives.

00:04:26.510 --> 00:04:30.470
And surely, some of you have
been moved by these things,

00:04:30.470 --> 00:04:31.700
as well.

00:04:31.700 --> 00:04:35.750
That kind of ethos,
that kind of direction,

00:04:35.750 --> 00:04:40.700
